The higher the quality of the ammo you use, the more damage you'll deal to the balloons! \n<color=#FF0000>(You can only enter ranged attack view in Geffen.)</color>

name: pet slingshot
description: The Animal Protection Association is committed to the study of monster taming. The Pet Slingshot is a great invention that was created while studying ways to determine exactly how much HP pets have. (Pet Slingshot Projectiles must be equipped to use this weapon. Pets hit take damage equal to a percentage of their HP. There is an upper limit to the damage taken. Not effective against Mini, MVP, and bosses).

name: nian outfit
description: An outfit designed to look like Nian.

name: royal rites uniform
description: Uniform worn by the royal family during formal events. Beautifully dignified.

name: archaeology clothes
description: Archaeologists wear this outfit. Ruins on this continent are full of risks, and depending on the wits alone is not going to work for an explorer.

name: steam expedition outfit
description: The outfit of the Steam Expedition, very durable and functional.

name: plush bear outfit
description: An outfit that's suited for students. It's youthful and sweet.

name: hot blooded costume
description: Uniform worn by hot blooded youths - although the style is retro, it still looks great today.

name: sugar buzz clothing
description: Bee style clothing. Produce sticky sweetness through hard work.

name: 梦游仙境时装
description: 薇拉看完一本童话书后有了新的灵感，以故事中主人公的形象为蓝本做出了这套服装。

name: 魅惑巴尼
description: 侍者兔套装的一部分，穿梭于杯盏之间的侍者自然应当是一道风景，抛弃怯懦的羞耻心，大胆展示最为魅惑的自己吧！

name: bamboo breeze outfit
description: The style of this outfit and the techniques used are fresh and original. The bamboo embroidery at the hem is hand-stitched at great cost.

name: raging flame outfit
description: Admired by many fashion experts for it's unique style. It is said to be created by a visitor from a different world.\n

name: summer swimsuit vitality
description: You can almost feel the sea breeze when you put on a cool summer dress.

name: night watch outfit
description: Prontera’s famous designer tried their best to create an outfit that integrates the Schwarzwald Republic industrial style. It’s both majestic and cool.

name: demon hunter outfit
description: Close fitting and lightweight, specially made for hunters who need to respond instantly to changes in the battlefield. It can not only protect the hunters from the sharp teeth and claws, but also hide their figures in the lightless abyss.

name: benimaru set
description: Clothing designed in Japanese style due to the influence of samurai culture in the past.

name: 深海探险潜水服
description: 使用前沿科技材料制作的潜水服，可以让你在水下保持温暖

name: prep school costume
description: Seemingly exotic clothing brought by traders from abroad. Its sleek design and high level of comfort made it immediately popular among the public.

name: 暖色晚霞
description: 冬天的被窝就像吃人的怪物，暖洋洋的睡衣就是被窝魔爪的延伸……拜托，别开门，也别开窗……

name: time to set sail sailor suit
description: Put on your sailor suit and swab the deck, matey! There are new adventures ahead!

name: 满贯速击时装
description: 全副武装的棒球比赛用套装，在球场上大显神威吧！

name: 活力之夏泳装
description: 夏天才会穿的清凉装扮，换上后仿佛已经感受到了海风的吹拂。

name: european server uniform
description: The well-tailored uniform exudes the calm and elegance of the last century. It will available after will be available to female characters after the update in 06.09.2022.

name: precious jade outfit
description: Simple but elegant ancient outfit. The jade ring above is as bright as the moon in the sky, expressing one’s feeling of missing.

name: diablo set
description: Full of respect and adoration for Rimuru. It's the perfect combination of absolute loyalty and great individual strength.

name: 心游宇宙制服
description: “身为最优秀的航天工程师之一，我认为宇航服的设计应该考虑实用性，而不是如何装下大量的玫瑰花和巧克力！”——工程师辛格·道格

name: 春日郊游时装
description: 春光明媚，清风和煦，是个适合郊游的好日子。小黄鸡背包里放着新鲜的便当，和伙伴们一起分享吧。

name: rimuru demon lord set
description: A powerful monster's proof of being recognized by the world. It's a symbol of a demon evolving to their peak.

name: shuna set
description: Clothing designed in Japanese style due to the influence of samurai culture in the past.

name: shion set
description: Full of respect and adoration for Rimuru. It's the perfect combination of absolute loyalty and great individual strength.

name: milim demon lord set
description: A powerful monster's proof of being recognized by the world. It's a symbol of a demon evolving to their peak.

name: hypebeast
description: A set of costume employed laser-reflective materials, ideal for light show. You will be the shining star in a well-lit night

name: 夜行小丑服
description: 传说中恐怖小丑们在入侵之夜所穿戴的装束，平常他们如同常人一般与人类共生，一旦夜幕降临光明褪去，他们就会显露恐怖的真貌。

name: og vibez
description: Wow! Who just enter the floor with that dazzling gesture? And who is stealing all the attentions in the club?

name: winter frost outfit
description: Designed by professionals to keep you warm all the way in the coldest weather. It is becoming a must-have for anyone who wants to climb the snow mountains.

name: wild vigilante
description: Injustices abound in the vast and sparsely populated wilderness, but vigilantes will not tolerate criminals! Get your equipment on, we're going after those felons!

name: 圣夜华服衣装
description: 在花车游行中必不可少的，就是演奏乐曲的乐团了，不仅声音要响亮，整齐也是必不可少的……当然，还有仅由训练有素的成员才能穿上的制服！

name: 窗边魔精衣装
description: 传说那位在圣夜不停奔走完成孩子们愿望的圣人有着一群忠实的伙伴，为他整理礼物、准备载具，还有……做晚饭。

name: chosen one costume
description: Take up a sword, bend a bow, mount a horse, until you're brave enough, so that I may repay Odin.

name: spring envoy tiger robe
description: It is not all about the traditional bright red design. It corresponds to the atmosphere of the New Year, and is also very suitable for other important occasions to dress up. The tiger starts the year and sends the news of spring by stepping on the clouds.

name: 候选食神制服
description: 不仅要驾驭各类食材，真正的大厨能将烹饪的过程化为赏心悦目的表演，这身工作服也是你的演出服，征服食客们的眼球和味蕾吧！

name: officer's suit
description: In the days when the gods walked the earth, this uniform symbolized peace and hope. Until the gods fell and monsters rampaged, it never changed.

name: kylin outfit
description: The high quality outfit from the ancient East to Midgard are decorated with accessories and motifs inspired by the “Kylin”, an auspicious beast that wards off misfortune and brings good luck to its owner.

name: sakura kimono
description: Flowers seldom encounter the snow. Your fancy dress touches the falling cherry blossom, facilitating the most fantastic reunion of flowers and snow.

name: 蜜蜂player
description: 01编写翅膀，芯片嵌入心脏，无边的数据洪流里，最后的玩家突然听见“嗡嗡”声。

name: master fishmonger set
description: The set for the king of fish market. Don’t interrupt the one in that set unless you want some exotic fish like blue fin tuna, leopard coral trout, or Chinese bahaba gutted and cleaned.

name: street artist set
description: Skateboard? Graffiti? Parkour? Put it on, you are the coolest artist on the street!

name: fluffy lion king
description: After a full meal, the Fluffy Lion King rubbed his small stomach, \"Huh? Where’d my muscles go? Mmm... but this feels really nice~

name: 十字军铠甲
description: 被瓦尔基里施以祝福的神圣铠甲，唯灵魂纯净之人才能穿上。

name: 武僧劲装
description: 简练贴身的武者劲装，适合多种战斗动作的施展。

name: training corps uniform
description: Recruit uniform of the Training Corp, with the emblem of sword and shield displayed on the left chest pocket, shoulders and back.

name: survey corps uniform
description: Uniform of the Survey Corps，with the emblem of dual-color wings displayed on the left chest pocket, shoulders and back.

name: cleaning outfit
description: Pristine cleaning outfit, suggesting the owner’s determination to sweep all the dust.

name: camping gear
description: Sturdy and durable camping gear that provides the best protection for campers.

description: Forged from the Asgardian Oridecon, the dwarven craftmanship used has been lost since the twilight of the gods.

name: gm uniform
description: What looks like the official uniform of some dimensional authority, which symbolizes protection and order.

name: 星之偶像礼服
